                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-171-defend1307 t18170416-171-punish905"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
